  The
  <b>
   Loop
  </b>
  action library contains those actions that are required for creating loops in your game action
    code. A loop is simply a way of iterating over the same set of actions 1 or more times depending on certain conditions and are handy in any situation where you need to repeat the same actions over and over again.
  
  
